title: Bug 5804Bug in ClassFileEditor.getCorrespondingElement
description: Bug 5804Bug in ClassFileEditor.getCorrespondingElement protected IJavaElement getCorrespondingElement(IJavaElement element) {IJavaElement parent= JavaModelUtil.findParentOfKind(element,IJavaElement.CLASSFILE);return (parent == this ? element : null);}'this' is a ClassFileEditor, so parent will never be 'this'
